Originally from Brisbane, the Greg Chappell Cricket Centre is a cricket retail business founded in 1973. Today, the Cricket Centre has 9 Australian locations in 5 major cities. Our international and rural customers view and purchase from our huge range online or order directly from our annual catalogue.

Here at the Cricket Centre we love the history, technology and effort that goes into every piece of cricket equipment. This labor of love drives us to constantly be on the look out for the next big thing. Whenever we find it, expect it to appear here and in our constantly updated online store
